            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Hd1e108">Rubrica 20</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De audacia timore spe et desperatione et magnanimitate bellatorum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#O"/>De audacia timore spe et de spe<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ratione 
               et magnanimitate bellatorum. Rubrica. 20.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e123">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e120">SAlustius in ca<!--line bumps up-->tilinario</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e129">Quanta cuiusque 
               <lb ed="#O"/>animo audacia natura aut moribus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>mesta tanta in bello patere solet. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>¶ Semper in bello his maximum 
               <lb ed="#O"/>est periculum qui maxime timent
               <lb ed="#O"/>Audacia promuro habetur. Neces<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>situdo 
               etiam timidos fortes facit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e146">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e145">UIrgilius eneide libro 2. in medio.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e150">Una salus uictis nullam spe<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>rare 
               salutem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e154">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e158">SEneca de <!--line bumps up--> naturalibus questionibus libro 3</ref> <!--line bumps back down--> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e162">nullus pernitiosi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>or 
               hostis est quam quem auda<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>cem 
               angustie faciunt longe uio<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>lentius
               semper ex necessitate quam ex 
               <lb ed="#O"/>uirtute confligitur aut certe paria 
               <lb ed="#O"/>conantur animus magnus et perditus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e170">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e178">FRontinus libro 4. titulo 5.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e174">C. l. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>Marcellus cum in manus gal<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>lorum 
               imprudens incidisset circun<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>spiciende 
               regionis qua euaderet 
               <lb ed="#O"/>cum equum in orbem flexit deinde esset
               <lb ed="#O"/>infesta uidisset deprecatus deos in 
               <lb ed="#O"/>medios hostes irrupit quibus in<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>opinata 
               audacia percussis ducem quoque 
               <lb ed="#O"/>eorum trucidauit. Atque ubi spes 
               <lb ed="#O"/>salutis uix superfuerat inde optima 
               <cb ed="#O" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#O"/>retulit spolia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e195">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e205">Ualerius <!--line bumps up--> maximus. libro 3. titulo de <!--line bumps back down--> fiducia sui</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e199">Sci<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>pio 
               emilianus uti spiritus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>egregius successor cum urbem pre<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ualidam 
               obsideret suadentibus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>quibusdam ut circa menia eius fer<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>reos 
               murices spargeret omniaquem ua<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>da
               plumbatis stabulis habentibus cla<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>uorum 
               cacumina consterneret ne 
               <lb ed="#O"/>subita irruptione hostes in presidia 
               <lb ed="#O"/>nostra impetu facere possent respon<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dit 
               non esse eiusdem et capere aliquos 
               <lb ed="#O"/>et timere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e228">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e240">UEgetius <!--line bumps up--> dere militari. libro 1. titulo 1.</ref> ¶ <!--line bumps back down--> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e232">Scientia rei bellice dimi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>candi 
               nutrit audaciam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e238"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e250">3 titulo.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e240">Minus mortem timet qui minus 
               <lb ed="#O"/>deliticarum nouit in uita.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e248"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e266">20 titulo.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e250">Necesse est ut acriorem dimicandi 
               <lb ed="#O"/>saniat audaciam qui munito pe<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ccatore 
               uel capite non timet uul<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>nera</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e258">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e281">libro 3. in prohemio:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e262">Nemo prouo<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>care 
               nemo audet offendere quem in<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>telligit 
               superiorem esse si pugnet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e271"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e293">
               <lb ed="#O"/>9. titulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e273">ad rem pertinet nosce quos animos 
               <lb ed="#O"/>aduersarii copie quos habeat noster ex<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>ercitus 
               que pars sibi magis uictoriam 
               <lb ed="#O"/>repromittat. eiusmodi enim cogitati<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>onibus 
               uirtus augetur aut frangi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>tur
               cauendum est ne dubitantem 
               <lb ed="#O"/>formidantemque exercitum ad pugnam 
               <lb ed="#O"/>publicam aliquando producas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e292"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e316">10. titulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e294">Qui 
               <lb ed="#O"/>autem longum tempus aut omnino nunquam 
               <lb ed="#O"/>uiderunt homines uulnerari uel occi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>di 
               cum primum aspexerint perhorrescunt 
               <lb ed="#O"/>et pauore confusi de fuga magis quam 
               <pb ed="#O" n="212-v"/>
               <cb ed="#O" n="a"/>
               <lb ed="#O"/>de conflictu incipiunt cogitare. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>Facilius est ad uirtutem nouos 
               <lb ed="#O"/>imbuere quam reuocare preteritos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e311"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e337">12. 
               <lb ed="#O"/>titulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e313">Ipsa die qua certaturi sunt mi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>lites 
               et cetera. Respondit. s. de prouidentia et
               <lb ed="#O"/>percon. ¶ Animis pene omnium hominum 
               <lb ed="#O"/>hoc naturaliter euenit ut trepident cum 
               <lb ed="#O"/>ad conflictum hostium uenerint sine 
               <lb ed="#O"/>dubio autem infirmiores sunt quorum 
               <lb ed="#O"/>mentes ipse confundit aspectus
               <lb ed="#O"/>Sed quo hec remedio formido leuitur 
               <lb ed="#O"/>si antequam dimices frequenter exer<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>citum 
               tuum locis tutioribus ordines 
               <lb ed="#O"/>Unde et uidere hostem et cognoscere 
               <lb ed="#O"/>consuescant interdum audeant.
               <lb ed="#O"/>Aliquid ex occasione aut fugient
               <lb ed="#O"/>aut interimant inimicorum mores 
               <lb ed="#O"/>aduersariorum arma equos reco<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>gnoscant 
               nam quae ex usu sunt 
               <lb ed="#O"/>non timentur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e353"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e381">22. titulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e355">Qui autem
               <lb ed="#O"/>congressum recedit ex acie suis fi<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>duciam 
               minuit et inimicis ad<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>dit 
               audaciam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e363"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e393">25. titulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e365">Nunquam exul<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>tantibus 
               maius solet euenire discer<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>mine 
               quam cum exhibita fortia in for<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>midine 
               commutantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e379"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e412">26 titulo. et finali.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e381">Nunquam ad certamen publicum perdu<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>xeris 
               militem nisi cum uideris eum spe<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>rare 
               uictoriam.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e390"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e424">libro 4. titulo 25.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e392">Ne<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>cessitas 
               quedam uirtutis est de<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>speratio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e400"> 
               <!--paragraph omitted-->
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e412">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e453">BAldo <!--line bumps up--> 11 fabula.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e416">Hic ope uir<!--line bumps back down-->tutis spes est ubi nul<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>la 
               salutis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e422">
               <!--line bumps down-->
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e465">GUalterius <!--line bumps up--> de castellione. libro 4.</ref> <!--line bumps back down--> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e426">Spes sane resusci<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>tat 
               egrum agmen et in 
               <cb ed="#O" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="#O"/>uultu uictoria uisa sedere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-d1e434">
               <lb ed="#O"/><ref xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Rd1e479">GUaufridus in poetria capitulo 30.</ref> 
               <lb ed="#O"/><quote xml:id="bHY6yh-e00673-Qd1e438">Sitimor incuruet mentem 
               <lb ed="#O"/>simulatio uultum. Erigat et clip<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>eo 
               uultus succurre timori. ymo 
               <lb ed="#O"/>magis sperare uelis pigeat pa<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>tentem.
               Uulgari pallere uultum
               <lb ed="#O"/>si posse sit artum. Dilates animum
               <lb ed="#O"/>si corpus debile mens sit. fortis 
               <lb ed="#O"/>et exiguas uires supplere memen<lb ed="#O" break="no"/>to. 
               Sepe grandi.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
